name: Tin Tin Mya
description: '''Tin Tin Mya''' ({{langx|my|တင်တင်မြ}}; born 25 April 1936) is a Burmese singer. She is best known for her classical songs. She acted one film named ''[[Ta Kyawt Hna Kyawt Tay Ko Thi]]'', directed by [[Win Oo]] and she also featured with song the same name of this film in this film.
